list.item:
Metabolic Syndrome [
                        see Warnings and Precautions (5.2)

                        ]

Advise patients that there is an increased risk of metabolic changes such as hyperglycemia, diabetes, hyperlipidemia, and non-alcoholic fatty liver disease with LUTRATE DEPOT therapy. Inform patients that periodic monitoring for metabolic changes is required when being treated with LUTRATE DEPOT [
                        see Warnings and Precautions (5.2)

                        ].
